gw.cc.claim.archiving.entity

Interface ClaimInfoSearchView

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ArchivedClaimCompatible

    public interface ClaimInfoSearchView
extends ArchivedClaimCompatible
    ClaimInfoSearchView Supports the efficient creation of claimInfo lists returned through ClaimCenter's search function. This is a virtual entity and is not stored in the database.
